--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gguf-tools (gguflib) — https://github.com/antirez/gguf-tools
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The C GGUF parser (fp16.c, gguflib.c) used by the kq.load_gguf loader is fetched
at build time and statically linked. gguf-tools is distributed under the MIT
License, Copyright (c) 2022 Georgi Gerganov. The full text accompanies the
upstream source.
